OL,5, Fast-growing health and beauty firm The
OL,6, Hut Group (THG) has confirmed plans to 
OL,7, overhaul its corporate governance after
OL,8, its share price crashed last week.     
OL,10,FA "golden share" that allowed founder  
OL,11,FMatthew Moulding control over takeovers
OL,12,Fand acquisitions is being removed.     
OL,14,FThe structure also stopped THG - which 
OL,15,Fowns Lookfantastic - joining the FTSE  
OL,16,F100 under UK listing rules.            
OL,18,FShares in THG, backed by Japan's       
OL,19,FSoftbank, plummeted 35% last week on   
OL,20,Finvestor concerns about the structure. 
